jeus.servlet.tcp

Class TCPServletRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • jeus.servlet.engine.HttpServletRequestImpl
      • jeus.servlet.tcp.TCPServletRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest, javax.servlet.ServletRequest

    public abstract class TCPServletRequest
extends jeus.servlet.engine.HttpServletRequestImpl
    TCPServlet.service(TCPServletRequest,TCPServletResponse)의 인자로 사용되는 클래스이다. javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest를 implements한 클래스로서 javax.servlet.ServletRequest, javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest의 모든 method를 호출할 수 있다. 그러나 TCPServlet의 특성상 method의 동작이 다를 수 있다.

      • getBody

        public byte[] getBody()
               throws java.io.IOException
        Deprecated. 
        Returns the body of incoming request packet.

        The length of the body is the result of TCPDispatcherConfig.getBodyLength(byte[]). If it is equal to or less than zero, this method returns null. If it is a long, which means that it's bigger than Integer.MAX_VALUE, you cannot use this method.

        If content length is too big, this method can cause OutOfMemoryError. Therefore, it is recommended to use HttpServletRequestImpl.getInputStream() and its read methods instead. But HttpServletRequestImpl.getReader() is not recommended because it is affected by request-encoding configuration.

        Returns:
        the request body
        Throws:
        java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException - if the length of body is a long
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if ServletInputStream is already used
        java.io.IOException - if an I/O error occurs.

        public java.lang.String getCharacterEncoding()
        javax.servlet.ServletRequest.getCharacterEncoding()을 override한 함수이다. 다음과 같은 우선 순위롤 선택된 값을 리턴한다.
        1. domain.xml
        2. javax.servlet.ServletRequest.setCharacterEncoding(String)으로 설정된 값
        3. domain.xml 를 제외한 값
